additional.message_body:
Good Morning,

 

Sending a friendly reminder that today will be your Orientation via Webinar that starts promptly at 2pm EST today. Please see webinar link below.

 

For anyone that have not sent in all their new hire paperwork and photo with their address for their ID badge to be sent, please forward directly to me prior to Orientation. Please also remember that everyone should start the onboarding process through the link that was emailed to you previously from ADP. Section 1 of the I9 through the onboarding is mandatory and should be completed within 3 days of your start date in order for your supervisor to complete section 2 of the I9 through ADP. We no longer accept paper I9 forms.

 

Thank you,
